%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%204%20Lakh%20For%20Hitjob%3A%20%26quot%3BLady%20Don%26quot%3B%20Behind%20Air%20India%20Crew's%20Chilling%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLady%20Don%26quot%3B%20Kajal%20Khatri%2C%20arrested%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Crime%20Branch%2C%20has%20confessed%20to%20organising%20Air%20India%20crew%20member%20Suraj%20Mann's%20killing%20in%20January%202023%20for%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20plot%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Naveen%20Sharma%2C%20who%20was%20paid%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20in%20advance%20for%20obtaining%20the%20weapons%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%20amount%20to%20be%20settled%20after%20the%20killing.%20However%2C%20the%20plan%20unravelled%20when%20Noida%20Police%20arrested%20Sharma%20before%20the%20full%20payment%20was%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20preparing%20to%20take%20swift%20action%20against%20Kajal%20under%20the%20Gangster%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20DCP%20Noida%20Police%20Manish%20Kumar%20Mishra%20said.%20Several%20more%20names%20have%20surfaced%20during%20the%20investigation%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20apprehend%20all%20involved%2C%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20Khatri%20revealed%20that%20she%20is%20married%20to%20Kapil%20Mann%2C%20a%20notorious%20gangster%20currently%20in%20jail.%20The%20two%20met%20in%20a%20gym%20in%20Sector-11%20of%20Delhi's%20Rohini%20and%20married%20in%202019.%20Since%20then%2C%20Khatri%20has%20been%20an%20active%20member%20of%20Kapil%20Mann's%20criminal%20enterprise%2C%20providing%20financial%20and%20logistical%20support%20to%20the%20gang.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20she%20met%20Kapil%20Mann%20in%20jail%20shortly%20before%20Suraj%20Mann'ss%20murder%2C%20where%20the%20detailed%20plan%20for%20the%20assassination%20was%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20of%20Suraj