eshow%2F113506200.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'd%20sworn%20off%20dating%20apps%20until%20I%20heard%20about%20the%20'burned%20haystack'%20approach%20women%20are%20swearing%20by.%20So%20I%20put%20it%20to%20the%20test.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20wearing%20a%20floral%20dress%20sitting%20in%20the%20park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eba779d17aa3c7b2b4095b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENicola%20Prentis%20thought%20she%20had%20given%20up%20on%20dating%20apps%20for%20good%20until%20she%20discovered%20a%20new%20method.%3Cp%3ENicola%20Prentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENicola%20Prentis%20thought%20she%20had%20given%20up%20dating%20apps%20for%20good.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20coming%20across%20Burned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method%20on%20Facebook%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20with%20100%2C000%20members%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20trying%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20single%20mom%2C%20using%20the%20new%20method%20helps%20her%20avoid%20online%20dating%20from%20taking%20up%20too%20much%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20two-and-a-half-year%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-celibacy-to-avoid-dating-apps-bumble-campaign-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20break%20from%20the%20time-suck%20of%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20reluctantly%20reinstalled%20one%20on%20my%20phone%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20I%20was%20determined%20not%20to%20waste%20hours%20swiping%20or%20replying%20to%20any%20zero-effort%20%26quot%3Bhi%2C%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20was%20inspired%20by%20Burned%20Haystack%2C%20a%20new%20dating%20method%20that%20encourages%20daters%20to%20filter%20out%20time%20wasters%20and%20red%20flags%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennie%20Young%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20English%20and%20women%20and%20gender%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Green%20Bay%2C%20had%20grown%20frustrated%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-is-a-dating-app-remote-work-online-romance-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooking%20for%20love%20online%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20she%20realized%20it%20was%20like%20looking%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bneedle%20in%20a%20haystack%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20decided%20to%20Google%20her%20question%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20find%20a%20needle%20in%20a%20haystack%3F%26quot%3B%20This%20led%20her%20to%20the%20answer%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20her%20method%3A%20Burn%20the%20haystack.%20That's%20what%20will%20make%20spotting%20the%20metal%20needle%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20method's%20main%20idea%20is%20to%20avoid%20focusing%20on%20being%20broadly%20appealing%20and%20not%20to%20try%20to%20meet%20as%20many%20men%20as%20possible.%20It's%20about%20being%20more%20selective%20about%20men%20and%20always%20weighing%20in%20on%20how%20they%20communicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20we%20immediately%20block-to-burn%20men%20who%20lead%20with%20comments%20about%20our%20appearance%20or%20with%20sexual%20content%20has%20absolutely%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20personal%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Young%20wrote%20in%20a%20Substack%20article%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20in%20August.%20Rather%2C%20she%20explains%20that%20they%20are%20blocked%20because%20those%20types%20of%20comments%20can%20lead%20to%20the%20following%20conclusions%3A%20poor%20social%20skills%2C%20lack%20of%20empathy%2C%20laziness%2C%20or%20disrespect%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20started%20the%20Facebook%20group%20Burned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method%20last%20year.%20It%20now%20has%20over%20100%2C000%20members%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f921649-14b9-4870-a48f-9ba38b3352c3%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20single%20mom%2C%20my%20time's%20too%20limited%20for%20swiping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20I%20treated%20the%20apps%20as%20a%20numbers%20game%20and%20talked%20to%20as%20many%20men%20as%20possible%20to%20get%20to%20the%20first%20meeting.%20With%20the%20net%20cast%20wide%2C%20surely%20I'd%20meet%20someone%20interesting%20sooner%2C%20right%3F%20But%20I%20found%20most%20guys%20would%20swipe%20right%20indiscriminately%20or%20send%20likes%20to%20every%20woman%20in%20the%20vicinity%2C%20so%20I%20was%20swamped%20with%20men%20who%20never%20even%20looked%20at%20my%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20to%20an%20actual%20date%20as%20it%20seemed%20messaging%20endlessly%20was%20the%20goal.%20Responding%20to%20matches%20and%20impersonal%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20how%20was%20your%20day%3F%26quot%3B%20messages%20became%20as%20exciting%20as%20filing%20utility%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-running-business-tips-work-life-balance-find-time-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle%20mom%20with%20my%20own%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20just%20didn't%20have%20time%20for%20more%20admin.%20So%2C%20after%20a%20few%20months%2C%20some%20unremarkable%20meet-ups%2C%20and%20one%20ghosting%20disaster%2C%20I%20deleted%20the%20apps%20for%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20only%20tempted%20back%20when%20I%20read%20about%20Burned%20Haystack%20and%20started%20connecting%20with%20other%20Facebook%20members%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20seemed%20just%20as%20fed%20up%20with%20online%20dating%20as%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ae5e36b-8786-4d86-a273-9503042da9f0%5C%22%3ENow%2C%20I%20use%20academic%20principles%20to%20select%20matches%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20teaches%20followers%20how%20to%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20in%20profiles%20and%20spot%20clues%20in%20photos.%20I've%20learned%20that%20everything%20tells%20you%20who%20the%20guy%20really%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBed%20selfies%20and%20requirements%20to%20be%20open-minded%20and%20adventurous%3F%20They're%20only%20interested%20in%20sex.%20A%20profile%20saying%20%26quot%3Bwe'll%20get%20along%20if%20you%20avoid%20unnecessary%20arguments%20and%20always%20live%20in%20the%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20mean%20easygoing%2C%20it%20means%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20committing%20for%20the%20future%20and%20you%20can't%20say%20anything%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%20If%20their%20perfect%20Sunday%20is%20watching%20Netflix%2C%20our%20future%20together%20would%20be%20spent%20in%20front%20of%20the%20TV%2C%20which%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20he's%20not%20the%20guy%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20in%20a%20green%20sweater%20sitting%20on%20a%20chair%20with%20a%20laptop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661cd93516bde8d4ead8d47c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20been%20connecting%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Facebook%20group%20Burned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method.%3Cp%3Ehoneyhousephotography.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20thing%20about%20the%20method%20is%20that%20I'm%20only%20on%20the%20app%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%20a%20day.%20Most%20of%20that%20time%20is%20spent%20narrowing%20the%20pool%20down%20by%20blocking%20or%20removing%20profiles%20that%20don't%20suit%20me%20or%20give%20off%20red%20flags.%20And%20I%20cross%20off%20anyone%20who%20sends%20a%20%26quot%3Blike%26quot%3B%20without%20a%20message%20because%20I%20know%20that%20%26quot%3Blike%26quot%3B%20isn't%20an%20indicator%20of%20genuine%20interest%20and%20only%20dilutes%20the%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%2C%20I%20would%20have%20looked%20at%20their%20profile%20and%20written%20a%20personalized%20message%20to%20those%20guys%20if%20I%20liked%20something%20on%20it.%20I'd%20have%20overlooked%20the%20generic%20intro%20message%2C%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20OK%20because%20it's%20the%20conversation%20afterward%20that%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20they%20didn't%20ask%20me%20any%20questions%2C%20I'd%20ask%20more%20to%20keep%20the%20chat%20going%20in%20case%20they%20actually%20wanted%20to%20meet%20and%20just%20weren't%20great%20at%20texting.%20Now%2C%20instead%20of%20suggesting%20meeting%20to%20speed%20things%20up%2C%20I%20block%20or%20remove%20their%20profile%20after%20a%20few%20days%20if%20they're%20stuck%20in%20virtual%20chat%20mode.%20If%20a%20chat%20dies%20on%20their%20side%2C%20I%20let%20it%20and%20never%20give%20them%20a%20second%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20such%20a%20relief%20that%20managing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomads-looking-for-love-dating-mistakes-to-avoid-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20taking%20over%20my%20life.%20Every%20day%2C%20when%20I%20clear%20the%20pool%20and%20there%20are%20no%20more%20profiles%2C%20I%20cheer%20inwardly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c91cec4b-a3a5-4327-9223-1e99c69bf9a8%5C%22%3EI'm%20translating%20the%20method%20to%20real%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20early%20days%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20method%20means%20the%20dating%20apps%20won't%20suck%20my%20will%20to%20live%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20it's%20taught%20me%20that%20the%20same%20signs%20are%20visible%20in%20the%20way%20a%20man%20speaks%20and%20how%20he%20behaves%20in%20person.%20If%20he%20talks%20about%20himself%20the%20whole%20date%2C%20he's%20not%20nervous%20about%20impressing%20me%3B%20he's%20a%20bad%20communicator.%20If%20he's%20late%20and%20doesn't%20message%20to%20let%20me%20know%2C%20he's%20not%20relaxed%3B%20he's%20inconsiderate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20new%20method%20working%3F%20With%20just%20those%20couple%20of%20minutes%20a%20day%20on%20the%20app%2C%20I've%20already%20had%20three%20in-person%20dates%20in%20three%20weeks%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20I'd%20happily%20meet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20personal%20essay%20about%20dating%20that%20you%20want%20to%20share%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20editor%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aakarplus%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eakarplus%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-new-method-online-burned-haystack-jennie-young-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726791242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaa91ace3009a0fac71e5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-new-method-online-burned-haystack-jennie-young-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Facebook%20group%20for%20the%20Burned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method%20was%20started%20by%20Jennie%20Young%20and%20now%20has%20over%20100%2C000%20members.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Nicola%20Prentis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-new-method-online-burned-haystack-jennie-young-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Splinter%20Cell%3A%20Deathwatch%E2%80%99%20Confirms%20Liev%20Schreiber%20as%20Sam%20Fisher%20in%20First%20Look%20at%20Netflix%20Anime%20Series%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726791060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fliev-schreiber.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236151253%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Liev%20Schreiber%20is%20Sam%20Fisher.%20Netflix%20has%20released%20a%20first-look%20teaser%20at%20its%20anime%20adaptation%20of%20%E2%80%9CSplinter%20Cell%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20confirms%20that%20the%20actor%20will%20be%20voicing%20Tom%20Clancy%