.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20sipping%20from%20Champagne%20flutes%20after%20popping%20the%20bottle%2C%20you're%20likely%20enjoying%20your%20bubbly%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstop-using-champagne-flutes-this-is-the-best-way-to-drink-champagne-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrong%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Richard%20Hemming%2C%20a%20master%20sommelier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHemming%20knows%20his%20sparkling%20wine%3A%20He's%20the%20head%20of%20wine%20at%2067%20Pall%20Mall%20Singapore%2C%20a%20luxury%2C%20members-only%20wine%20club%20and%20restaurant.%20And%20he's%20not%20totally%20against%20flutes%3A%20He%20used%20them%20at%20his%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlutes%20have%20become%20the%20standard%20for%20Champagnes%20because%20they're%20small%2C%20easy%20to%20hold%2C%20and%20convenient%20for%20serving%20%E2%80%94%20though%20not%20the%20easiest%20to%20pour%2C%20since%20fizz%20means%20they%20need%20to%20be%20topped%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they're%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20for%20appreciating%20the%20wine%2C%26quot%3B%20Hemming%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long%2C%20narrow%20shape%20of%20the%20iconic%20glassware%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-glass-to-drink-champagne-from-is-not-a-flute-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estifles%3C%2Fa%3E%20Champagne's%20aroma%20and%20flavor%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it's%20hard%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20tip%20way%20too%20far%20back%20to%20actually%20drink%20the%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20Hemming%20told%20BI.%20The%20narrow%20opening%20concentrates%20the%20bubbles%2C%20making%20it%20a%20nightmare%20to%20pour%20and%20a%20challenge%20to%20enjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226449%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Champagne%20served%20in%20flutes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d1879c1d8d2deb96b7931c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22