they're%20just%20plain%20awkward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Reddit's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fiphone%2Fcomments%2F1eg71co%2Fwhat_triggered_siri_to_tell_me_to_start_a_checkin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20r%2FiPhone%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20someone%20said%20their%20phone%20recently%20suggested%20they%20do%20a%20Check%20In%20with%20their%20ex%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20person%20couldn't%20figure%20out%20why.%20Someone%20else%20followed%20up%20with%20a%20similar%20horror%20story%3A%20%26quot%3BJust%20happened%20to%20me%20too.%20We've%20been%20no-contact%2C%20she%20lives%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20away%2C%20and%20we%20haven't%20been%20sharing%20locations%20in%20months.%20I%20somehow%20accidentally%20accepted%20the%20check-in.%20I%20threw%20up%20lmao.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevicetalkforum.com%2Ft%2Fwhat-triggered-siri-to-suggest-i-check-in-with-my-ex%2F580%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevice%20forum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20someone%20reported%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20using%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevicetalkforum.com%2Ft%2Fwhat-triggered-siri-to-suggest-i-check-in-with-my-ex%2F580%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EiPhone%2013%20Pro%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Max%2C%20and%20out%20of%20nowhere%2C%20Siri%20suggested%20that%20I%20start%20a%20Check%20In%20with%20my%20ex.%20The%20thing%20is%2C%20we're%20currently%20no-contact%2C%20and%20this%20has%20never%20happened%20with%20any%20of%20my%20other%20contacts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fguide%2Fiphone%2Fuse-check-in-iphc143bb7e9%2Fios%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%20user%20support%20forums%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20people%20are%20similarly%20stumped%20about%20the%20logic%20behind%20who%20is%20suggested%20in%20the%20Siri%20alerts%20for%20Check%20Ins.%20They're%20also%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20disable%20the%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20ever%20get%20a%20fix%20for%20this%3F%20Mine%20has%20just%20started%20and%20recommended%20I%20share%20my%20location%20with%20my%20older%20male%20boss%2C%20and%2C%20yeah%2C%20I%20can't%20see%20a%20single%20thing%20in%20any%20of%20the%20settings%20to%20turn%20it%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20forum%20poster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20didn't%20respond%20to%20questions%20from%20BI%20about%20what%20leads%20to%20a%20suggested%20contact%20for%20a%20Check%20In%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20how%20to%20turn%20it%20off.%20And%20despite%20my%20best%20efforts%2C%20I%20couldn't%20find%20a%20good%20answer%20for%20how%20to%20turn%20off%20these%20Check%20Ins%20without%20turning%20off%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsiri-apple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESiri%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggestions%20in%20iOS18.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20suggestions%20are%20actually%20fairly%20reasonable%3A%20Siri%20suggesting%20you%20check%20in%20with%20a%20spouse%20or%20sibling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKylie%20Robison%2C%20a%20reporter%20at%20The%20Verge%2C%20noticed%20she%20had%20been%20getting%20these%20suggestions%20to%20Check%20In%20with%20her%20mother%20when%20she%20got%20home%20after%20midnight.%20%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20was%20not%20my%20emergency%20contact%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20text%20her%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20probably%20not%20the%20most%20out%20of%20any%20contact%3F%26quot%3B%20Robison%20is%20still%20confused%20about%20why%20an%20adult%20who%20doesn't%20live%20with%20her%20mother%20is%20getting%20suggestions%20that%20she%20text%20her%20mom%20at%201%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20gotten%20these%20Check%20In%20suggestions%2C%20but%20a%20friend%20told%20me%20he%20gets%20a%20suggestion%20to%20Check%20In%20with%20his%20friend%20Max%20when%20he%20bikes%20near%20his%20apartment%20on%20his%20morning%20commute.%20But%20the%20suggestion%20isn't%20mutual%20%E2%80%94%20Max%20told%20m