20link%20between%20the%20two%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e820ee0-9d48-47a1-ac3b-d143921c5807%5C%22%3EBen%20Affleck's%20ancestors%20hail%20from%20Scotland%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ben%20affleck%20casey%20affleck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F546a673a69bedd016accbdf8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBen%20and%20Casey%20Affleck.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FChris%20Pizzello%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20just%20so%20happens%20that%20I%20am%20both%20an%20avid%20fan%20of%20the%20Hulu%20show%2C%20and%20had%20already%20traced%20Ben%20Affleck's%20family%20tree%20on%20Ancestry.com%20for%20fun%20several%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20there%20was%20a%20minor%20scandal%20when%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fthetwo-way%2F2015%2F06%2F25%2F417455657%2Fafter-ben-affleck-scandal-pbs-postpones-finding-your-roots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBen%20Affleck%20had%20pressured%20producers%20of%20the%20PBS%20genealogy%20show%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BFinding%20Your%20Roots%26quot%3B%20to%20edit%20out%20any%20mention%20of%20a%20slave-owning%20ancestor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20genealogy%20buff%20myself%20who%20has%20occasionally%20tried%20doing%20celebrity%20family%20trees%20for%20fun%2C%20I%20was%20curious.%20(The%20slave%20owner%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20great-great-great%20grandfather%20on%20his%20mother's%20side).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20work%20already%20done%2C%20I%20was%20already%20halfway%20there%20with%20being%20able%20to%20verify%20a%20cousin%20relationship%20with%20the%20reality%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Ben%20and%20Casey%20Affleck%20are%20famously%20from%20Boston%2C%20their%20Affleck%20side%20of%20the%20family%20is%20not%20from%20Massachusetts.%20Their%20father%20and%20grandfather%2C%20Myron%20Affleck%2C%20Jr.%2C%20were%20born%20in%20Rhode%20Island.%20The%20next%20two%20generations%20back%20of%20Afflecks%20were%20from%20Yonkers%2C%20New%20York.%20Finally%2C%20we%20get%20to%20William%20Affleck%2C%20born%20in%201824%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland%2C%20who%20immigrated%20to%20Yonkers%20in%201848%20and%20worked%20in%20the%20railroad%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20his%201906%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesmachine.nytimes.com%2Ftimesmachine%2F1906%2F03%2F13%2F101769594.html%3FpageNumber%3D9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobituary%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20Zac%20Affleck's%20side%2C%20his%20male%20Affleck%20ancestors%20have%20been%20in%20Utah%20for%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20search%2C%20I%20found%20no%20overlap%20or%20common%20ancestry%20between%20the%20two%20Affleck%20families%20in%20the%20United%20States%20going%20back%20to%20the%201800s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(For%20transparency%2C%20information%20about%20Zac's%20living%20father%20and%20grandfather%20came%20from%20newspaper%20notices%20and%20other%20public%20records.%20For%20older%20generations%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20U.S.%20Census%20records%2C%20birth%20and%20death%20records%2C%20and%20other%20records%20available%20on%20Ancestry.com).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225dd73755-8f19-4e73-9a7c-06adf00e6b89%5C%22%3EZac%20Affleck's%20ancestors%20had%20strong%20ties%20to%20powerful%20Mormons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC3v-9I3M4bJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC3v-9I3M4bJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC3v-9I3M4bJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Jen%20Affleck%20(%40jenniferlaffleck)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EZac%20Affleck's%20family%20does%20have%20a%20very%20interesting%20history%2C%20arguably%20far%20more%20interesting%20than%20merely%20being%20related%20to%20a%20famous%20actor.%20The%20Affleck%20family%20arrived%20in%20Utah%20sometime%20between%201871%20and%201880%20from%20the%20city%20of%20Preston%20in%20Lancashire%2C%20England.%20Preston%20is%20notable%20for%20having%20the%20oldest%20continually%20running%20congregation%20of%20the%20LDS%20church.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthechurchnews.com%2Fliving-faith%2F2024%2F07%2F23%2Fpreston-ward-branch-longest-continually-running-unit-church%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPreston%20branch%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20established%20by%20missionaries%20in%201837%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decade%20before%20the%20Mormons%20settled%20in%20Utah%20in%201847.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Preston%20Affleck%20was%20born%20in%201801%20in%20Scotland%20and%20moved%20to%20England%20sometime%20before%201825%2C%20eventually%20settling%20in%20Preston.%20According%20to%20a%20written%20family%20history%20by%20a%20relative%2C%20William%20converted%20to%20the%20new%20religion%20after%20meeting%20missionaries%20there.%20Although%20he%20died%20before%20being%20able%20to%20leave%20England%2C%20he%20urged%20his%20children%20and%20wife%20to%20go%20to%20%26quot%3BZion%26quot%3B%20(Utah)%2C%20where%20they%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20branches%20of%20Zac's%20family%20also%20have%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20church.%20His%20fifth%20great-grandfather%2C%20William%20Smith%20Muir%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Scotland%20in%201822.%20Muir%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Mormons%20who%20followed%20Joseph%20Smith%20to%20Nauvoo%2C%20Illinois%2C%20and%20later%20went%20to%20Utah.%20Muir%20was%20a%20notable%20pioneer%2C%20enough%20so%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Flifeofwilliamsmi00muir%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E166-page%20family%20history%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20him%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsouthwickresearch.com%2FGenealogy%2FWilliam%2520S%2520Muir%2520Coloring%2520Book-11.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren's%20coloring%20book%20about%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20impossible%20to%20say%20definitively%20that%20Zac%20Affleck%20and%20Ben%20Affleck%20are%20not%20very%20distant%20cousins.%20It's%20possible%20they%20shared%20a%20common%20relative%20in%20Scotland%20from%20before%201800.%20As%20Scottish%20surnames%20go%2C%20Affleck%20isn't%20the%20most%20common%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20not%20incredibly%20rare%20(I%20have%20a%20great-great-grandparent%20with%20the%20last%20name%20Affleck%2C%20for%20example)%20and%20there%20are%20Afflecks%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20sharing%20a%20last%20name%20is%20a%20pretty%20good%20clue%20that%20there%20may%20be%20a%20family%20connection%20somewhere%20in%20history%2C%20it's%20not%20certain.%20The%20origins%20of%20the%20Affleck%20surname%20date%20back%20to%20the%201200s%2C%20so%20there%20are%20centuries%20of%20