sands%20storming%20the%20Presidential%20palace%20which%20was%20then%20occupied%20by%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe's%20predecessor%20Gotabaya%20Rajapaksa%2C%20who%20fled%20the%20country.%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20took%20charge%20and%20restored%20calm%20and%20helped%20revived%20the%20economy%20by%20taking%20some%20tough%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20election%20is%20key%20to%20deciding%20the%20future%20of%20reforms%20in%20the%20economically%20fragile%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20his%20vision%20for%20future%20ties%20with%20India%20holds%20a%20stronger%20economic%20relationship.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20encourage%20more%20investments%20from%20India%20and%20more%20tourists%20from%20India.%20We%20are%20working%20together%20with%20India%20on%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20the%20Trincomalee%20Harbour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20over%20as%20President%20when%20the%20country%20was%20in%20utter%20chaos%20and%20no%20one%20thought%20we%20could%20stabilise%20this%20fast.%20But%20I%20knew%20from%20experience%20that%20we%20could%20go%20ahead%20provided%20we%20had%20the%20support%20of%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20and%20our%20creditors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20ensured%20we%20come%20back%20to%20normalcy.%20Law%20and%20order%20is%20functioning%2C%20democracy%20is%20functioning%20and%20although%20we%20have%20stabilised%20the%20economy%2C%20now%20we%20have%20to%20decide%20our%20path.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20get%20into%20the%20same%20old%20ways%20or%20are%20we%20working%20towards%20(building)%20a%20strong%20export%20economy%3F%20I%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20mandate%20to%20go%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20faces%20a%20tough%20electoral%20battle%20from%20two%20contenders.%20In%20total%2C%20President%20Wickremesinghe%20