-requirement-it-secretary-124091901389_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fgovt-may-allow-more-compute-capacity-based-on-requirement-it-secretary-124091901389_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengal%20Doctors%20End%20Cease-Work%2C%20To%20Resume%20Essential%20Services%20From%20Saturday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20doctors%20of%20Bengal%20called%20off%20their%20massive%20protest%20over%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20colleague%20at%20a%20Kolkata%20hospital%20and%20said%20they%20will%20join%20work%20from%20Saturday.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20caveat%20-%20they%20said%20they%20will%20not%20join%20OPD%20services%20or%20attend%20elected%20operations.%20These%20would%20be%20resumed%20once%20they%20are%20assured%20of%20the%20state%20government's%20commitment%20to%20the%20safety%20issue%2C%20they%20said.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20state%20had%20accepted%20most%20of%20their%20demands%20--%20and%20amid%20massive%20floods%20in%20south%20Bengal%20where%20health%20services%20have%20become%20a%20priority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20been%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20flood-hit%20areas%20since%20yesterday.%20It%20was%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20who%20attended%20the%20last%20meeting%20with%20the%20doctors%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20accepted%20their%20demands%20and%20suggestions%20regarding%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20he%20wrote%20to%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20giving%20detailed%20instructions%20which%20included%20ensuring%20adequate%20availability%20of%20on-duty%20rooms%2C%20washrooms%2C%20CCTVs%2C%20deployment%20of%20police%20and%20security%20personnel%20which%20would%20include%20women%2C%20mobile%20police%20teams%20for%20surveillance%20at%20night%2C%20central%20helpline%20and%20panic%20buttons%20and%20alarms.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20has%20also%20ordered%20an%20audit%20of%20%C2%A0security%20at%20all%20state-run%20medical%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20this%20partial%20return%20to%20work%20is%20not%20by%20any%20means%20an%20end%20to%20their%20agitation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20needed%2C%20we%20will%20begin%20ceasework%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20junior%20doctors.%20The%20legal%20battle%20will%20also%20continue%2C%20as%20would%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20quick%20resolution%20of%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20that%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20this%20phase%20of%20protest%20will%20be%20marked%20by%20a%20march%20from%20the%20protest%20site%20to%20the%20CGO%20Complex%2C%20where%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20is%20located.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20of%20the%2041-day%20impasse%20with%20the%20state%20government%20was%20set%20in%20motion%20on%20Monday%2C%20with%20the%20doctors%20sitting%20face-to-face%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20three%20failed%20attempts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20had%20immediately%20announced%20the%20removal%20of%20Kolkata%20police%20chief%20Vineet%20Goyal%20and%20two%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20health%20department.%20The%20doctors%2C%20though%2C%20are%20still%20pushing%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20health%20secretary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20they%20say%20they%20will%20go%20and%20discuss%20and%20then%20will%20decide%20on%20lifting%20the%20ceasework.%20But%20I%20have%20requested%20them%20to%20do%20so%2C%20citing%20the%20condition%20of%20patients%2C%20especially%20in%20view%20of%20the%20floods%20in%20some%20of%20the%20districts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20said%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20had%20declared%20that%20meeting%20a%20%26quot%3Bpartial%20success%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20government%20was%20capitulating%20in%20face%20of%20the%20protests%20that%20was%20buttressed%20by%20thousands%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2031-year-old%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20on%20August%209.%20The%20prime%20suspect%20is%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20with%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20who%20was%20stationed%20at%20the%20police%20outpost%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20had%20access%20to%20all%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20that%20started%20at%20the%20hospital%20the%20next%20day%20soon%20snowballed%2C%20drawing%20in%20%C2%A0the%20civil%20society%20and%20leading%20to%20a%20massive%20logjam%20with%20the%20state%20government%20that%20could%20not%20be%20resolved%20even%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bback%20to%20work'%20order%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20though%20the%20court%20order%20has%20empowered%20her%20to%20use%20strong-arm%20tactics%2C%20she%20would%20not%20do%20so%2C%20since%20she%20did%20not%20support%20%26quot%3BEmergency'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20logjam%20was%20caused%20by%20the%20police%20investigation%20that%20left%20too%20many%20unanswered%20questions%2C%20allegations%20that%20the%20police%20had%20forced%20the%20cremation%20despite%20the%20parents'%20unwillingness%20and%20an%20officer's%20offer%20of%20money%20to%20the%20woman's%20parents%20to%20bury%20the%20case.%20The%20officer%20concerned%20has%20been%20removed%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20state's%20transfer%20order%20for%20Principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20hours%20after%20he%20resigned%20from%20the%20post%20under%20pressure%20of%20public%20opinion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sequence%20of%20events%20led%20to%20spiralling%20protests%20that%20spread%20across%20the%20country%2C%20already%20outraged%20over%20the%20shocking%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726769220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ffd6d56n8_