s-sinks-after-explosive-blaze-in-california-marina%2Famp_articleshow%2F113499716.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ammunition%20From%20India%20Diverted%20To%20Ukraine%3F%20What%20Government%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDismissing%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20claiming%20that%20ammunition%20sold%20by%20Indian%20manufacturers%20has%20been%20diverted%20to%20Ukraine%20by%20European%20customers%20and%20New%20Delhi%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20trade%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20termed%20it%20%26quot%3Binaccurate%20and%20mischievous%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20questions%20on%20the%20report%2C%20MEA%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20the%20Reuters%20report.%20It%20is%20speculative%20and%20misleading.%20It%20implies%20violations%20by%20India%2C%20where%20none%20exist%20and%2C%20hence%2C%20is%20inaccurate%20and%20mischievous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20India%20has%20an%20impeccable%20track%20record%20of%20compliance%20with%20international%20obligations%20on%20the%20export%20of%20military%20and%20dual-use%20items%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20been%20carrying%20out%20its%20defence%20exports%20taking%20into%20account%20its%20international%20obligations%20on%20non-proliferation%20and%20based%20on%20its%20own%20robust%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20framework%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20holistic%20assessment%20of%20relevant%20criteria%2C%20including%20end-user%20obligations%20and%20certifications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%2C%20Reuters%20cited%20conversations%20with%20eleven%20Indian%20and%20European%20government%20and%20defence%20industry%20officials%20and%20an%20analysis%20of%20commercially%20available%20customs%20data%20to%20claim%20that%20artillery%20shells%20sold%20by%20Indian%20arms%20manufacturers%20had%20been%20diverted%20to%20Ukraine%20by%20European%20customers%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%20did%20not%20intervene%20to%20stop%20the%20trade%20despite%20protests%20from%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20the%20supply%20of%20munitions%2C%20which%20have%20helped%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20war%20against%20Russia%2C%20had%20been%20happening%20for%20over%20a%20year%20and%20the%20Kremlin%20had%20raised%20the%20issue%20with%20India%20at%20least%20twice%2C%20including%20in%20July%2C%20during%20a%20meeting%20between%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20his%20Russian%20counterpart%20Sergei%20Lavrov.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20Indian%20arms%20export%20regulations%20specify%20that%20weaponry%20can%20be%20used%20only%20by%20the%20declared%20purchaser%20and%20future%20sales%20to%20them%20can%20be%20stopped%20if%20there%20are%20unauthorised%20transfers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20Indian%20government%20and%20two%20defence%20industry%20sources%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Delhi%20produced%20only%20a%20very%20small%20amount%20of%20the%20ammunition%20being%20used%20by%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20one%20official%20estimating%20that%20it%20was%20under%201%25%20of%20the%20total%20arms%20imported%20by%20Kyiv%20since%20the%20war.%20The%20news%20agency%20couldn't%20determine%20if%20the%20munitions%20were%20resold%20or%20donated%20to%20Kyiv%20by%20the%20European%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20the%20European%20countries%20sending%20Indian%20munitions%20to%20Ukraine%20are%20Italy%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20an%20initiative%20to%20supply%20Kyiv%20with%20artillery%20shells%20from%20outside%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Spanish%20and%20a%20senior%20Indian%20official%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20former%20top%20executive%20at%20Yantra%20India%2C%20a%20state-owned%20company%20whose%20munitions%20are%20being%20used%20by%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726764000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.co