0to%20stay%20engaged.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20waste%20a%20minute%20of%20my%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20situation%2C%20as%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20earn%20a%20good%20income%20while%20pursuing%20what%20I%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20running%20a%20home%20business%20at%2056%2C%20Beena%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20pursuing%20your%20interests%20makes%20you%20happy%2C%20the%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20hectic.%20I%20enjoy%20my%20time%20doing%20this.%20With%20kids%20being%20away%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20farming%20and%20this%20home%20business%20that%20has%20become%20a%20medium%20for%20us%20to%20get%20engaged%20and%20get%20away%20from%20loneliness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20time%20is%20a%20precious%20commodity%2C%20Beena%20emphasises%20that%20pursuing%20one%E2%80%99s%20passions%20not%20only%20enriches%20one%E2%80%99s%20life%20but%20also%20positively%20impacts%20several%20others.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20met%20someone%20new%2C%20they%20would%20first%20ask%20my%20name%3B%20the%20second%20thing%20would%20be%20what%20I%20did%20for%20a%20living.%20Every%20person%20has%20a%20purpose.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20mine.%20These%20questions%20kept%20bothering%20me.%20But%20today%20as%20a%20working%20woman%20earning%20an%20income%2C%20my%20self-esteem%20has%20definitely%20grown.%20I%20feel%20confident%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20as%20we%20conclude%20our%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee.%20All%20photos%3A%20Beena%20Tom.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726662935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fbees-of-beena-3-1726661514.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala-based%20Beena%20Tom%20uses%20her%20cooking%20skills%20to%20make%20a%20variety%20of%20dishes%20from%20flowers%20and%20fruits%20availab