essible%20through%20a%20unique%20partner-led%20model%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20Siddharth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20battery%20swapping%20technology%20does%20for%20the%20electric%20mobility%20sector%20in%20India%20is%20address%20anxieties%20over%20the%20cost%20of%20EVs%20(since%20batteries%20make%20up%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%20of%20the%20production%20cost%20of%20a%20typical%20EV)%2C%20lack%20of%20adequate%20charging%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20time%20taken%20to%20charge%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279874%2Felectric-vehicles-sustainable-india-battery-reuse-recycling-renewable-energy-ev%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ee-mobility%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%20dominated%20by%20two%20and%20three-wheelers%20that%20are%20primarily%20deployed%20for%20public%20transit%2C%20freight%20transport%2C%20and%20last-mile%20delivery%2Fconnectivity%2C%20battery-swapping%20technology%20makes%20more%20sense.%20With%20smaller%20vehicles%20comes%20a%20requirement%20for%20batteries%20that%20are%20lighter%20to%20carry%2C%20and%20therefore%20swap.%20Also%2C%20drivers%20of%20these%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20charge%20their%20vehicles%20and%20can%20instead%20swap%20their%20old%20batteries%20for%20charged%20ones%20in%20a%20few%20minutes.%20These%20features%20are%20especially%20useful%20for%20fleet%20operators%2C%20last-mile%20delivery%20persons%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pulkit%20Khurana%2C%20co-founder%2C%20discusses%20his%20venture%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthekredible.com%2Fblogs%2Fbattery-smart-recorded-a-7-4x-spike-in-revenue-in-fy23%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecorded%20a%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Rs%2063.5%20crore%20in%20FY23%2C%20and%20their%20journey%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-12-1726583051.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EV%20Battery%20Swapping%20Technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-12-1726583051.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-12-1726583051-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-12-1726583051-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-12-1726583051-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-12-1726583051-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366327%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBattery%20Smart%20swapping%20station%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlugging%20gaps%20in%20the%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpending%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20in%20the%20logistics%20and%20shared%20mobility%20sectors%2C%20and%20engaging%20in%20policy%20consulting%20before%20establishing%20Battery%20Smart%2C%20Pulkit%20and%20Siddharth%20regularly%20gathered%20information%20about%20the%20e-mobility%20sector.%20They%20learnt%20that%20there%20were%20major%20gaps%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20over%202.5%20million%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F276266%2Fdr-anil-rajvanshi-wins-padma-shri-invents-electric-rickshaw-alcohol-stove%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20rickshaws%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20were%20powered%20by%20lead-acid%20batteries%2C%20serving%20nearly%2070%20million%20people%20for%20first%20and%20last-mile%20commutes.%20We%20recognised%20that%20high%20upfront%20costs%20were%20a%20significant%20barrier%20to%20adopting%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20a%20cost-conscious%20market%20like%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Pulkit%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLead%20acid%20batteries%20require%20replacement%20every%20six%20months%2C%20making%20it%20a%20recurring%20capital%20expenditure%20problem%20for%20drivers.%20Moreover%2C%20drivers%20often%20spend%2010%20to%2012%20hours%20every%20night%20charging%20their%20batteries%20and%20another%203%20to%204%20hours%20to%20top%20it%20up%20during%20the%20day.%20Our%20goal%20was%20to%20upgrade%20the%20existing%20solution%20with%20better%20technology.%20Battery%20swapping%20emerged%20as%20the%20solution%2C%20as%20it%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20end%20users%20to%20own%20the%20battery%2C%20reducing%20upfront%20costs%20by%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20multiple%20ventures%20at%20the%20time%20that%20decided%20to%20get%20into%20the%20business%20of%20manufacturing%20EVs%20and%20chargers%2C%20Pulkit%20and%20Siddharth%20ventured%20into%20battery-swapping%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20manufacturing%20chargers%20and%20vehicles%20is%20an%20exciting%20field%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20addressing%20key%20challenges%20such%20as%20range%20anxiety%2C%20charging%20downtime%2C%20and%20high%20costs.%20By%20partnering%20with%20over%20ten%20leading%20OEMs%20(original%20equipment%20manufacturers)%20working%20on%20battery%20development%20and%20manufacturing%2C%20we%20can%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20with%20changing%20technology.%20We%20always%20have%20the%20option%20to%20evaluate%20and%20choose%20from%20the%20best%20battery%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EV%20battery%20swapping%20technology%20works%20better%20than%20straight%20charging%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366328%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20Battery%20Smart%20Swap%20Station%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20Battery%20Smart%E2%80%99s%20swapping%20stations%20operate%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Pulkit%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20interoperable%20batteries%20for%20electric%20two%20and%20three-wheelers%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20easily%20locate%20the%20nearest%20swapping%20station%20via%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20app.%20Our%20goal%20at%20Battery%20Smart%20is%20to%20build%20a%20dense%20network%20of%20swap%20stations%20by%20ensuring%20EV%20users%20are%20within%20a%20one-kilometre%20radius%20of%20a%20station%20with%20zero%20wait