2%80%9CThe%20vehicles%20have%20smart%20meters%2C%20which%20indicate%20to%20the%20users%20when%20to%20swap%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20%E2%80%94%20from%20locating%20the%20nearest%20swap%20station%20to%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20done%20on%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20batteries%20they%20deploy%2C%20Pulkit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20we%20use%20are%20smart%20and%20interoperable%2C%20making%20them%20compatible%20with%20electric%20three%20and%20two-wheelers.%20These%20batteries%20are%20produced%20by%20different%20battery%20manufacturers%20but%20are%20identical%20in%20specifications%20and%20dimensions.%20This%20means%20that%20from%20a%20customer%E2%80%99s%20perspective%2C%20the%20same%20model%20of%20batteries%20is%20being%20swapped.%20We%20source%20our%20batteries%20from%20over%2010%20Lithium-ion%20battery%20OEMs%20in%20India%20based%20on%20their%20recent%20track%20record%20to%20ensure%20quality%20and%20reliability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20much%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20set%20up%20one%20battery%20swapping%20station%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20mentioned%2C%20we%20have%20a%20partner-led%20model%2C%20where%20we%20leverage%20the%20existing%20infrastructure%20and%20collaborate%20with%20local%20businesses%20to%20set%20up%20swap%20stations%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace%2C%20without%20the%20need%20for%20commissioning%20new%20real%20estate%20and%20can%20now%20open%20three%20to%20four%20stations%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20usually%20takes%20six%20weeks%20for%20a%20station%20to%20go%20live.%20Our%20partners%20only%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20licensing%20fee%2C%20while%20the%20rest%2C%20including%20all%20investments%20in%20chargers%20and%20batteries%2C%20is%20done%20by%20Battery%20Smart.%20Through%20this%20model%2C%20the%20partners%20are%20typically%20able%20to%20break%20even%20on%20their%20upfront%20fee%20within%20one%20year%20and%20get%20three%20years%20to%20operate%20under%20the%20standard%20agreement.%20Currently%2C%20through%20our%20partner%20network%20of%201%2C200%20swap%20stations%2C%20we%20do%20one%20lakh%20swaps%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEnsuring%20compatibility%20with%20different%20EV%20models%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20battery-swapping%20venture%20catering%20to%20two%20and%20three-wheeler%20EVs%2C%20how%20does%20a%20venture%20like%20Battery%20Smart%20ensure%20such%20compatibility%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20offer%20batteries%20through%20a%20Battery-as-a-Service%20model%2C%20we%20enable%20users%20to%20overcome%20common%20barriers%20to%20EV%20adoption.%20These%20batteries%20we%20use%20are%20interoperable%20and%20serve%20over%20200%20vehicle%20models%20with%20a%20single%20type%20of%20battery.%20So%2C%20while%20they%20may%20be%20produced%20by%20different%20OEMs%20the%20specifications%20and%20dimensions%20will%20be%20uniform%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20swappable%20batteries%20are%20around%202%20to%202.5%20kWh%20in%20capacity%2C%20and%20weigh%20about%2012%20to%2015%20kg.%20The%20smaller%20batteries%20result%20in%20lower%20weight%20of%20the%20electric%20two-wheeler%20and%20yield%20better%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20greater%20range%20on%20the%20available%20charge.%20An%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333931%2Fbengaluru-startup-converts-petrol-two-wheeler-to-hybrid-electric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20two-wheeler%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20designed%20to%20run%20with%20one%20battery%2C%20whereas%20vehicles%2C%20such%20as%20e-rickshaws%20and%20e-autos%2C%20can%20be%20fitted%20with%20up%20to%20two%20such%20batteries%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20energy%20consumption%20and%20range%20requirements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20goes%20on%20to%20state%2C%2