-college-1726051697-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Soumya%20Chakraborty%20left%20behind%20her%20life%20in%20Kolkata%20to%20spearhead%20the%20Nagaland%20medical%20college.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudying%20in%20their%20home%20state%20was%20not%20an%20option.%20You%20see%20for%2061%20years%20since%20attaining%20statehood%20in%201963%20%E2%80%94%20the%20state%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Assam%20following%20Independence%20%E2%80%94%20Nagaland%20did%20not%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F283733%2Fdoctor-madhusudan-gupta-first-human-dissection-asia-medicine-history-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20medical%20college%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20approved%20NIMSR%20to%20take%20in%20its%20first%20batch%20of%20100%20MBBS%20students%20for%20its%20inaugural%20academic%20session%202023-24.%20The%20youth%20of%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20saw%20this%20decision%20as%20a%20lifeline%20to%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20brightest%20minds%20of%20his%20batch%2C%20Zavi%20recalls%20the%20monumental%20decision%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20relieved.%20The%20other%20option%20would%20be%20to%20move%20to%20Assam%20or%20Shillong%20to%20attend%20the%20medical%20college%20there.%20Studying%20in%20the%20same%20state%20where%20I%20was%20born%20makes%20me%20feel%20fortunate%3B%20I%20feel%20lucky%20to%20be%20among%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20medical%20students.%20The%20fact%20that%20I%20live%2030%20minutes%20away%20from%20college%20feels%20amazing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0