%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20requested%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20then%20labour%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20to%20set%20up%20the%20medical%20college%20in%20Bihar%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Soumya%20states.%20Now%20known%20as%20ESI%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Bihta%2C%20she%20shares%20that%20while%20the%20college%20was%20sanctioned%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%202019%20and%20the%20construction%20had%20been%20completed%2C%20the%20college%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20started%20functioning%20yet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sent%20there%20by%20the%20labour%20ministry%20to%20start%20the%20college%20as%20founder%20dean%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Soumya%20conceded%20to%20go.%20When%20asked%20how%20she%20managed%20the%20project%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20she%20simply%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20collaboration%20and%20cooperation%20by%20the%20State%20Government%20helped%20expedite%20things.%20I%20have%20realised%20that%20barriers%20can%20always%20be%20overcome.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20take%20challenges%20and%20turn%20them%20into%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReeling%20from%20this%20success%2C%20Dr%20Soumya%20returned%20to%20her%20role%20as%20dean%20in%20Kolkata.%20But%20then%20she%20got%20a%20call.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BBhupender%20Yadav%5D%20was%20keen%20that%20I%20go%20to%20Nagaland%20and%20help%20set%20up%20the%20medical%20college%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Family%20is%20important%3B%20career%20is%20too%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Espoke%20to%20six%20individuals%20from%20Nagaland%20to%20get%20their%20insights%20on%20one%20question%3A%20Do%20you%20feel%20alienated%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20stood%20out%20for%20me%20was%20how%20many%20of%20the%20responders%20said%20that%20their%20fear%20of%20discrimination%20had%20forced%20them%20to%20live