22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plugzmart%3A%20IIT-M%20Incubated%20Startup%E2%80%99s%20Fast%20EV%20Charger%20Takes%2030-45%20Mins%20to%20Charge%20Electric%20Cars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPlugzmart%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Chennai-based%20original%20equipment%20manufacturer%20(OEM)%20of%20EV%20chargers%20%E2%80%94%20obtained%20certification%20for%20its%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20charger%20from%20the%20Automotive%20Research%20Association%20of%20India%20(ARAI)%20late%20last%20month.%20ARAI%20is%20a%20research%20institute%20with%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Heavy%20Industries%2C%20which%20develops%20standards%20for%20vehicles%20and%20their%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20important%20development%20in%20advancing%20an%20indigenous%20EV%20infrastructure%20in%20India%20given%20how%20it%20has%20been%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F280479%2Findia-electric-vehicle-revolution-ev-charging-infrastructure-network-experts-future%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0unable%20to%20keep%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20the%20growing%20fleet%20of%20domestic%20EVs.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20indigenous%20manufacturing%20of%20its%20(charging%20infrastructure)%20key%20components%20is%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20does%20the%20ARAI%20certification%20mean%20for%20Plugzmart%E2%80%99s%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%3F%20This%20certification%20for%20the%20Chennai-based%20startup%E2%80%99s%20fast%20charger%20and%20proprietary%20controller%20card%20signifies%20their%20compliance%20with%20stringent%20operational%20safety%20standards%20and%20efficiency%20norms%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307090%2Fchennai-startup-builds-homegrown-iot-enabled-smart-ev-chargers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2F